{"tid":25360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"控制校內電腦成偷窺狂 小學IT男今認罪","createTime":"2016-12-06T05:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T18:33:01.000Z","uid":10338,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"301539b53b8fb2fef01fc4e8ac4dd321ed53072a","tid":25360,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:39:50.000Z","msg":"跑馬地寶覺小學前男電腦技術員承認於2011至2014年在職期間，擅自偷入小學的電腦終端機，於4名女教師的桌上及手提電腦內安裝黑客系統，利用電腦的鏡頭偷窺對方及偷拍裙底，甚至於離職後仍在家遙距干擾學校電腦。技術員今於區院認罪，控方需時整理案情，案件將於明天續審。<br />\n<br />\n被告盧景順（36歲）承認8項目的在於使其本人或他人不誠實地獲益而取用電腦、有犯罪意圖而取用電腦及刑事毀壞罪，獲准繼續保釋候判。"},{"pid":"0cb969f875871233976e0e4a55f29e064d149b56","tid":25360,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:41:55.000Z","msg":"睇錯以為而家啲小學生咁撚勁識hack人部腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c271767a180cc19c00f734696efb44121b8d53","tid":25360,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:44:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇錯以為而家啲小學生咁撚勁識hack人部腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n+1"},{"pid":"c4d6e1147f1f36389225ae6c82b77583b4920378","tid":25360,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:45:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇錯以為而家啲小學生咁撚勁識hack人部腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n+1</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n+2"},{"pid":"f17e2f7d006d17a909a8819280cd283918fd888f","tid":25360,"uid":36861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:46:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇錯以為而家啲小學生咁撚勁識hack人部腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n+1</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n+2</blockquote><br />\n+3"},{"pid":"aee0a4f84d87c295d37604be42e8e7f8214ba6b7","tid":25360,"uid":25619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:48:24.000Z","msg":"<blockq